{"tid":2211722,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"林鄭：「為省時所以用中國建築，沒有經過招標」；羅致光：「為了省時所以用中銀，沒有經過招標。」","createTime":"2020-09-21T10:01:32.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-21T15:38:14.000Z","uid":230104,"like":73,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"ff9ab9d48c4f8ad3c0dd3ccaf30a76c9e337644c","tid":2211722,"uid":230104,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:01:32.000Z","msg":"相信林鄭政府，未來都不會招標，而且會同中國既官方採購方式接軌，還會經常化， 閹割ICAC都係為了免阻頭阻勢<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n果班當年投左林鄭票既香港建築公司老闆，我真係恭喜你地呀，你地作為condom可以返返出去了<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n用共企黨企可以用來換政治本金，點會用你班香港佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"637d5bbeed5aa2d15f25066646e24d09eb29280c","tid":2211722,"uid":286897,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:04:06.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"50ea43616f5bb797e8833a5c4ae60694d6d5a77c","tid":2211722,"uid":97080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:04:43.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fcd78b9e17a1e89d9d942687ac17977b9b120a33","tid":2211722,"uid":143241,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:05:14.000Z","msg":"為慳時間所以唔戴套,中出內射唔使射到一地都係."},{"pid":"27772707bc6ac373e158b6809e63adbbbd5a003f","tid":2211722,"uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:06:37.000Z","msg":"再玩埋定向招標，中銀、建行、工商三間選一間，夠晒公平公正<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5646216caac8f5602568b218180315c8bdfb1e10","tid":2211722,"uid":17008,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:07:05.000Z","msg":"省時 咪 即係加速囉 其實岩丫<br />\n<br />\n省時主義"},{"pid":"209d6fd7ca3bb5376da60c9c68fbfeefe86a2257","tid":2211722,"uid":230104,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-21T10:08:30.000Z","msg":"聽講匯胸同揸打仲打算不理美國二級制裁都要狗衝林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr